    """
    Retrieve configuration data from an external source and validate its cryptographic signature.

    Args:
        config_filename: The name of the configuration file to retrieve.
        crypt_signature: The cryptographic signature to validate.

    Returns:
        A dictionary of configuration data if the signature is valid; otherwise, None.
